snippet.title: Metal Slug Anthology [Full Game | No Commentary] PS4
snippet.description:
Metal Slug Anthology Full Game Walkthrough No Commentary 1080p 60fps played on the PlayStation 4

Completed the game doing everyone game in Metal Slug Anthology with the help of DeSeRTxEaGLe-420 (except for Metal Slug X which I played solo). Metal Slug Anthology is a great game filled with the best co-op run and run games around. It's so much fun playing this with a friend. Metal Slug 4 is my favorite. Hope you enjoyed this video.
